This building, surrounded by a big garden and a pond, is the former novitiate ('noviciaat' in Dutch) of Scheut. All the missionaries started their 7 years of studying in this place. It was a first year of trial to see if they wanted to continue becoming a missionary. Today the building serves as a retirement home for old missionaries.
